| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2355 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a0ebc3db-3fa5-5db1-9680-8ca59d50159f"
